Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該去自首\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You should turn yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽見了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你一直過著什么樣的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know what kind of life you've been living,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但肯定沒多風光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it can't be much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是五十步笑百步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Said the pot to the kettle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What-- That is--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荒謬至極  你竟然對我說教\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is really rich, you-- You preaching to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不知道我做過或沒做過什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See, you have no idea what I did or didn't do, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說了  你怎么不去自首\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A-And why don't you turn yourself in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你那么有罪惡感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}seeing as how you're the one with the guilty conscience, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么阻止了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What-- What is stopping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗林死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fring's in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麥克死了  拉羅也死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mike's in the ground. Lalo's in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必為了我而猶豫不決\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't have to hold back on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們只能處死我一次  所以你盡管去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They can only hang me once. So-- So go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全說出來  自我懲罰吧  看對你有什么好處\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Spill your guts! Put on your hair shirt, see what it gets you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金  我們為什么說起自首\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kim, why are we even talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都很聰明  不會無緣無故毀掉自己人生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're both too smart to throw our lives away for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just... I only wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高興你還活著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm glad you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該唱歌了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Time to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*祝你生日快樂*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*Happy birthday to you*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*祝你生日快樂*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*Happy birthday to you*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*祝你生日快樂  親愛的譚美*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*Happy birthday, dear Tammy*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*祝你生日快樂*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*Happy birthday to you*
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}阿爾布開克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法官讓你走之前我不能離開\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't leave before the judge dismisses you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證讓他們知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll make sure they're aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就記住坐直身子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, just remember to sit up straight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法官跟你說話時認真聽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and listen carefully when the judge addresses you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持專心  注意力集中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay attentive and engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你不確定發生什么事了  也別表現出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even if you're not so sure what's going on, don't show it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把襯衫下擺掖進褲子里去  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Tuck your shirt in for me, will you? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要給法官一個好印象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You gotta look good for the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你有前科\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because of your record...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  謝麗爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, Cheryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在門口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}塞拉曼加離開后不久  吉米和我就開始謀劃一次長期行動  讓人懷疑霍華德·哈姆林的品格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}為了私利...\N破壞霍華德...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}假造他可卡因成癮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}塞拉曼加進入了我們家...  頭部中槍  霍華德立即死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我按照指示  開車去弗林家\N厄門紹特毀滅證據...\N...偽裝成自殺...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍華德是被人殺害的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Howard was murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不該在那時出現在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the wrong place at the wrong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的尸體在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where's his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會再搜尋嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will they search again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They'll search.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得他們應該找不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think they'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝麗爾  他...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cheryl, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都發生在一瞬間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It-- it all happened in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒有受苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he didn't-- he didn't suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他沒有受苦"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"He didn't suffer."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倆編出的謊言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The lies you two made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們描繪出的那個他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The picture you painted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在完全是那個人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人只記得那樣的他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all anybody remembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想改變現狀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來會怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happens now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會受審嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will you be tried?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會坐牢嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will you go to jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是律師  對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a lawyer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個了不起的律師  霍華德說的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a-- A great one, Howard said!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How could you not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.56,0:23:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把宣誓口供交給了伯納利歐縣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bernalillo County has my affidavit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否起訴要看地檢官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's up to the district attorney whether to prosecute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可能不會起訴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And she may not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有確鑿證據\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no physical evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我的前夫以外沒有證人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No remaining witnesses other than my ex-husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.52,0:23:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我的前夫還活著的話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}assuming he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.15,0:23:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以在民事法庭起訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could sue you in civil court.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.59,0:23:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以拿走你的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could take everything you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.01,0:24:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.57,0:24:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么這么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.81,0:26:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.33,0:29:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}投資報告
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.33,0:29:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密碼  密碼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Passwords. Passwords...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.56,0:32:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個帽子收藏家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A hat man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.51,0:33:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}自由奔跑吧  銹銹
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.09,0:33:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.20,0:34:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里沒什么好看的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing to see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.25,0:34:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.61,0:36:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看這破玩意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look at this bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.67,0:36:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.44,0:36:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  你管這叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look. What would you call this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.84,0:36:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd call that...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.55,0:36:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I dunno, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.06,0:36:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫魚肉玉米卷餅嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you call that a fish taco?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.12,0:36:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰管這叫魚肉玉米卷餅啊  合法嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could anybody call this a fish taco? I mean, legally?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.12,0:36:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在我面前晃悠它了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop waving that thing at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.16,0:36:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.56,0:36:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一片鱈魚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's one piece of goddamned pollock
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.63,0:36:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒我大拇指尖大呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}no bigger than the end of my thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.85,0:36:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能管它叫...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, how can you even call that a--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.39,0:36:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我說有用嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like am I s'posed to do something?
