Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.16,0:54:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是索爾·古德曼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi. I'm Saul Goodman.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.42,0:54:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你有權利嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you know that you have rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.33,0:54:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憲法說你有  我也說你有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Constitution says you do, and so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.21,0:54:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信  在被證明有罪之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe that, until proven guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.32,0:54:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個國家所有的男人  女人  小孩都是無辜的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}every man, woman, and child in this country is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.67,0:54:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我會為你而戰  阿爾布開克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that's why I fight for you, Albuquerque!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.75,0:54:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.20,0:54:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.73,0:54:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩  你覺得這是我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Marion, do you think that's me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.22,0:54:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Cause it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.53,0:54:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從來就沒有咬咬  對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There never was a Nippy, was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.76,0:54:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰夫跟你說什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What did Jeff tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.34,0:54:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他什么也沒說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, he didn't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.89,0:54:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是搜索引擎告訴我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ask Jeeves told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.50,0:55:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輸入了"騙子"和"阿爾布開克"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I typed in "Con man" and "Albuquerque,"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.08,0:55:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的大名就跳出來了  明晃晃的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and up you popped, big as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.06,0:55:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么  瑪麗恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you doing, Marion?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.10,0:55:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說呢  我要報警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you think I'm doing? I'm calling the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.22,0:55:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  我來幫你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here, lemme help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.59,0:55:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  我想我們應該\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen, I think we're losing sight
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.80,0:55:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,著眼于大局  對不對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of the bigger picture here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.44,0:55:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰夫現在有麻煩  而我想幫他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jeff is in trouble, and I wanna help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.78,0:55:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他都需要你的支持\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He and I sure could use your support here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.72,0:55:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我兒子卷進什么事里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What did you get my son into?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.42,0:55:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是他自愿做的一些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing that he didn't ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.69,0:55:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.66,0:55:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是你認識的那個好朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm still the good friend you thought I was, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.50,0:55:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰夫理解我  巴迪理解我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jeff understands me, Buddy understands me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.06,0:55:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也會理解我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.97,0:55:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是  你得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just, you have to, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.36,0:55:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要節外生枝  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know, keep things on an even keel, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.67,0:55:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手里拿的什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What have you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.48,0:55:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它放下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Put that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.76,0:56:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下  瑪麗恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Put that down, Marion.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.66,0:56:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Put it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.71,0:56:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這么做  瑪麗恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do not do it, Marion.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.44,0:56:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次警告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Final warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.15,0:56:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信任過你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.43,0:56:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩  我是生命警報的瓦萊麗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Marion? This is Valerie with Life Alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.50,0:56:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.49,0:56:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  瓦萊麗  我不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, Valerie, I'm not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.76,0:56:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個罪犯正站在我的廚房里  威脅我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a criminal standing in my kitchen, threatening me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.33,0:56:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是一個通緝犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's a wanted man,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.89,0:56:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫索爾·古德曼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and his name is Saul Goodman!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.39,0:56:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  瑪麗恩  我來報警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, Marion, I'm calling the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.30,0:56:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就撥電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm calling right now.

